node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax How I hit a 6 figure income only a a few months after graduating from high school. (A thread)'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax First of all I want to make it very clear that I'm not sharing this to brag. I simply want to share my story and hope you get some value from it. So let's get started...'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In school, I was never the popular kid, I didn't have many friends and didn't really fit in. In fact, was getting severely bullied from 7th grade up until finishing high school. A few times it got to the point where we had to get the police involved.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax Although school wasn't really an easy time for me, looking back, those times made me more independent and sparked my interest in business and personal development.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In high school, came across a social media marketing agency course. I realized could start that business because it didn't require a huge starting capital and I could do it while I was still at school So I started my own agency.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In my last year of high school, started making $1-3K per month with my agency. It was nothing special but it was decent money at the time and it solidified that could eventually pursue my business full time.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So in the final year of high school, had two options, either go to university or learn a trade. I never really saw myself pursuing either of those things and decided to start working full time on my marketing agency once I eft school.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax I mostly got criticized for that but didn't care and believed that I made the right decision. So in September 2019, graduated from high schoo and my agency was making $1-3K at the time.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax By the end of 2019, scaled my agency to $20K per month. In 2020 I had my record month of $80K. And in 2021 I've scaled my agency past $100K per month.'.

Photo shared by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So that is the story of how I've built my agency over the past 2 years. If you'd like to learn more about building a social media marketing agency, drop a follow. me'.
Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Behind every strong person is a story that gave them no choice.'.
